OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FA 15-year-old girl is in a critical
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital after getting
OL,8,Finto difficulty in the sea during the
OL,9,Fheatwave on Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FFormby Beach, on the Sefton coastline,
OL,13,Fat around 3:30pm on Monday, 25 May,
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of a concern for the
OL,15,Fsafety of the teenager.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
