FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779991869
OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FIt is understood that members of the
OL,7,Fpublic rescued her from the water
OL,8,Fbefore she was taken to Alder Hey
OL,9,FChildren's Hospital, where she remains
OL,10,Fin a critical condition, Merseyside
OL,11,FPolice say.
OL,13,FOfficers are continuing to support her
OL,14,Ffamily as enquiries get underway to
OL,15,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,16,Fwhat happened.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
