OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779991869
OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Alan Nuttall
OL,7,Fstated that the beach was
OL,8,F"exceptionally busy" at the time and
OL,9,Furged anyone who saw what happened to
OL,10,Fcontact authorities immediately.
OL,12,FDCI Nuttall said: "I would appeal for
OL,13,Fanyone who witnessed this incident or
OL,14,Fhas any information which could assist
OL,15,Four enquiries to get in touch as a
OL,16,Fmatter of urgency.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
