OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779991869
OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,F"Our officers and I would also like to
OL,7,Foffer our gratitude to the members of
OL,8,Fthe public who came to the assistance
OL,9,Fof the 15-year-old girl and her family
OL,10,Fduring such tragic circumstances on
OL,11,FFormby beach.
OL,13,F"At this stage we believe the girl got
OL,14,Finto difficulties in the water and
OL,15,Fmembers of the public came to her aid.
OL,17,F"Emergency services were alerted and
OL,18,Fthe girl was taken to hospital where
OL,19,Fshe remains in hospital in a critical
OL,20,Fcondition."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
