PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779991869
OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FSeven children and two adults have
OL,7,Fdied in separate open water incidents
OL,8,Fover the Bank Holiday weekend amid
OL,9,Frecord-breaking temperatures across
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FMerseyside Police say they will
OL,13,Fcontinue to work alongside partner
OL,14,Fagencies - including Sefton Council,
OL,15,Fthe National Trust, HM Coastguard, and
OL,16,Fthe RNLI - to ensure the public can
OL,17,Fenjoy the coastline and beaches safely.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
