OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779991869
OL,3,CTeenage girl in critical condition
OL,4,Cafter getting into difficulty in sea
OL,6,FThe force is reminding visitors that
OL,7,Fit is vital to check the tides and
OL,8,Flifeguard advice before entering the
OL,9,Fwater, and to remember the RNLI's
OL,10,F'Float to Live' guidance if they find
OL,11,Fthemselves getting into difficulty.
OL,13,FIt also issued a plea to drivers,
OL,14,Fnoting that officers and other
OL,15,Femergency services need space on the
OL,16,Froads to get their vehicles to
OL,17,Fincidents. Visitors are asked to park
OL,18,Fresponsibly and avoid blocking roads
OL,19,Fand driveways.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
